My city is very big. It has many different kinds of people. Residential areas and commercial areas are mixed together. There are many businesses, like offices and stores, and restaurants. You can find many places to eat and shop. Some stores are big and well-known. Others are small and new. They are called boutiques. Some boutiques are in malls. Others are on the street.

My neighborhood is very diverse. There are people from different countries and cultures. We have a place for the LGBTQ+ community. We also have a Jewish community and a community of people from the Soviet Union. Nearby, there are many neighborhoods for people from other countries. We have Korea town, China town, and Little Armenia.

But the city is so big that it takes a long time to get from one place to another. It can take two hours to go 10 miles. Many people do not walk. They drive. The city has a lot of traffic. It is hard to find a parking spot. There are many new buildings being built. But some people do not want more people to move in.

There are many kinds of houses in my neighborhood. Not everyone lives in a big apartment building. Some people live in single-family homes or duplexes. The neighborhood has people of all ages. I do not know most of my neighbors. We are not a very close community. But I have good memories of playing outside with my friends when I was a child.

My neighborhood is interesting. Most houses are for one family. But some houses are split into two, but still connected. My house has a small front yard and a driveway on the left side. It looks like many other houses here. They remind us of a time when living in the suburbs was a good life. Many people thought this was the American dream. But now it is not as good as it was. My neighborhood is still the same, but some things are not. The people are not as happy. The yards are not as nice. But there are still cars in every driveway. Children still play outside. The public school has been here for almost 90 years. It still makes young people think about the future. It makes older people feel happy and sad at the same time. There are not many churches, and some are empty. But the basketball courts are always full. All the houses look different, but feel the same. There is a big store called Super A. It is owned by a big Yemni family. They are probably the only Arab family in the neighborhood. Most people in the neighborhood are African American. The streets are wide. Children play football. They only stop to let cars go by. Many people have lived here for many years. They can tell stories of a time when everyone knew everyone. There was a karate school. But when the kids stopped watching karate movies, the school became a pharmacy. There is a small movie theater. It shows old movies at a low price. The young people do not like it because it does not have new movies. But older people like it. They think it is a good way to spend an evening. There is a big road that goes through my town. But the entrance and exit are in the town next to ours. Some people wanted to put an exit in our town. The young people wanted it. But the older people did not. They thought it would ruin the town. So the city said no. We are building a new school. We are trying to choose a symbol for our town. I think a cyborg with a country accent and a cabin would be a good symbol.

You might not notice it at first. It is behind a shopping strip. But if you go behind the old Whole Foods and walk back behind the hotels, you will find a community. There are apartments on these streets. They are like small buildings. They are next to each other.

Some of these apartments are not good places. We will not talk about them. But the others are different. They are near a school that teaches adults. The school is quiet and sleepy. Students go inside with coffee and start their day.

The gate of the school creaks open. Commuters are unhappy because it slows down traffic. There is a park across the street. People walk their dogs there. Children play in the park. They run and jump. Old people walk their dogs and look at the teenagers on skateboards.

There is a store that sells sushi. It is in a shopping area. There is a store for pools and a store for nails. You can get a manicure while buying a pool. There is a store for frozen yogurt. Teenagers eat frozen yogurt and ride their skateboards.

This is a nice place. It is a small part of America. Not much changes here.

"This is everywhere," she said while we drove past the corn fields. "This is it!" I said. She was surprised by the open space. She came from a town where the grocery store was close to her house. She had never seen so much open space before. I knew she would be surprised. I grew up in a rural area of Ohio. I wanted to tell her about it. In that moment, she understood who I was and where I came from.

We drove down a country road. There was a quarry on the left. It was full of water. Behind the quarry was the place where I live. The houses are made of brick and stucco. They have a lot of space. We take care of the land around our houses. In the spring, there are flowers and trees. The driveways have nice cars. My neighbor was outside. He was mowing his lawn. He was singing. He is a friendly man.

My neighbor used to be a doctor. He is older now. He is not as quick as he used to be. He has a special history. He takes care of his lawn. He uses a big mower. Everyone likes him.

We will soon reach my house. There are geese in the yard. They are chased by our dog. There is a stream behind the house. It goes into the quarry. You can hear frogs and the stream. You can also hear animals from the nearby farms.

There is a special place behind the house. It is an oasis. There are trees and wildflowers. I spent a lot of time here as a child. I built forts and chased animals. I had friends in the neighborhood. The winters can be very cold. But they are also beautiful. The trees are bare. It looks empty. Sometimes it snows. Then it looks like a winter wonderland. My sister made snow angels in the yard. We built snowmen. We used snowballs to fight. We built forts to keep our things safe. We played in our own little world. We were happy and did not worry about anything."

Portland, Oregon is a city that values being different. The city's slogan is "Keep Portland Weird." For some, this means remembering the past when Portland was smaller and less expensive. In those days, the city had its own unique culture. Today, people come to Portland to be different and be accepted as different. However, this also means the city has grown more expensive and crowded. Many new buildings have been built to house people from California.

Portland is different. It means the city accepts things that are not normal. But it also has modern things like other cities. We buy many things from China like other parts of the country. Portland has yoga, hipsters, and business people. It is just that we do not take things too seriously.

In my neighborhood, people have colorful houses and gardens. In the summer, you can find free things on the sidewalk. These are boxes with items people no longer want. You can find clothes, books, or other things. Sometimes you can find something special. This is what Portland is like to me. But everyone is different. Some people like to do yoga with goats or watch soccer games. Other people like to try new things.

Portland has problems. Some people have drug problems. These problems often come from mental health issues. The rain and gray skies may also be a problem. Portland also has people who do not have homes. The city offers services to help them, but it is not enough. People who do not have homes and people who do have homes do not always agree on what to do.

There are mountains in the north. They are always there. The sun rises over them every day. The mountains are a big part of my life. I see them when I am happy and when I am sad. They help me when I am feeling anxious. I first saw the mountains when I came to this town for school. The university is nice with its buildings and ponds and trees. But the mountains are special to me. I like to visit them when I need to think. The town is also nice. There are many cafes where I study. The downtown area is old and beautiful. It has old buildings with colorful bricks. This part of town is busy like a big city. But if I walk a little further, I can find a quiet place. The library is near the quiet place. The town has two different feelings. One part is busy and one part is quiet. This is what makes this town special. I have many good memories here. I like walking in the park with friends. I like going to the movies in the theater. But I also have bad memories. Sometimes I go to the pond to think and feel sad. The pond is a good place to think and cry. While I watch the animals at the pond, I think about my life and my place in it. I wonder what I am supposed to do with my life. I walk to the main street and see the sun shining. I look at the mountains and feel strong. The mountains remind me to keep going.

If you visit Bensonhurst, Brooklyn, you will have no problem finding it. Many people use public transportation, and it is easy to get around New York City. Bensonhurst is a city neighborhood, so you will feel like you are in New York. You will see many Asian stores. Many Asian people live in Bensonhurst, and this is why you will see many Asian stores. They sell food, laundry service, and other things. These stores are popular because the food is good, prices are low, and it is easy to shop.

You will see many Asian-owned businesses in Bensonhurst. But this is not a neighborhood just for Asian people. Many people from other countries live here, and their children were born in the United States. There is a park near here with basketball courts, a soccer field, and swings for children. The park is good for people of all kinds.

Most houses in Bensonhurst are small homes, not big buildings. Many people live in apartments or houses with two families. The people here are nice, but they can be noisy. Cars often drive by with loud music, and people may leave dog waste on the ground. If you visit at night, be careful. There are some people who might cause trouble. There are also people who steal packages and dogs that are not cleaned up after. If you visit, watch where you walk.

I live in a place where there are not many sidewalks. The road goes up and down a big hill. My house is at the top of the hill. People call it the "exercise hill" because many people like to run up it. There are no sidewalks on my street, so people walk on the road. The road has some holes and can be difficult to drive on. Telephone and electric wires are hung around the neighborhood. They look old. Sometimes strong wind and rain break the wires. This makes the wires look broken. There are many tall trees everywhere. But people do not like the trees. They want to cut them down because they block the view of the ocean. Many houses are built high on the hill. They have big windows to see the ocean. It is nice to see the ocean at sunset. The water looks nice and the sky turns orange. But it is often cloudy and rainy here. The sunlight is blocked by the cloud. The sun does not shine every day. It is often overcast and damp. Moss grows on everything. It even grows on my car. I left my car outside for a month and it became green and hairy with moss. It took me three hours to clean it. There are not many children in my neighborhood. There is a school near my home. But most people in my neighborhood are old and retired. They have dogs instead of children. Dogs run in the street and sometimes enter homes through open doors and windows. It is common to see dogs in lawns and streets. Rabbits are also in the area. They dig up gardens and lawns. My cats like to hunt the rabbits and have chased most of them out of our neighborhood. We also see many birds, including small birds and big birds of prey. They fly over the area until the neighborhood crows chase them away. There are no stores near my home. But if I walk down the hill to the waterfront, I can find some restaurants that serve fresh seafood. There is no big beach, but it is fun to throw rocks into the water. The bay is not very wide. I can see the other side of the bay even on cloudy days.

I live in a small town in Tennessee. My home is on a street that connects two highways. This means we see more cars than I like. But it's a quiet neighborhood. People move in and out slowly. I know most of the people living here. They work in their yards and do daily tasks. In the winter, we sled down a small hill on our street. Our house is at the front corner of the street. We see everyone who comes and goes. We know the cars that people drive. 

There are four of us: me, my wife, and two daughters, aged eleven and fourteen. We work from home. This means we are at home a lot. People in the neighborhood know us. We go outside and play. We also grill on our back deck. You can smell barbecue. There are many trees in our neighborhood. It used to be a wooded area. This means there is a lot of shade. But in the fall, there are many leaves. We must rake and burn them. I like the smell of burning leaves. It means fall has arrived. 

Our garage is at the back of our house. We use the front door only when someone knocks. I like to work in the garage. When I open the garage doors, I feel connected to the neighborhood. The neighborhood is quiet on holidays. People visit with family and friends. There are many cars on the street during these times. I like living here. If it weren't a through street, it would be perfect.

My neighborhood is in the desert. It is very dry. There is a lot of dirt. If you have not lived here, you may not know what it is like. You see brown everywhere. It is hard to see a green lawn here. When I lived here in the 1990s, houses were far apart. Now, there are more houses. It looks like a city. But it is still a small town. Most people are friendly. There are good and bad things about this town. I like my neighborhood. It is nice because the old people are friendly.

There are many stores here. Most are big stores with similar products, like Food for Less and Smart & Final. If you want a special store, you have to go somewhere else. We do not have stores like Whole Foods here.

Many people work in construction. Our town is still growing. There are many open spaces left to build. I like it the way it is now. I moved from a big city, and I do not want to go back.

My job is in construction. I put up drywall and install T-bars.

I like my home because of the animals. People come to the desert for its beauty. The desert has many animals. We must learn about these animals to live safely and happily in the desert. My children love the animals. They are trying to catch lizards and bugs now.

There are things to do here. Victorville is a good place for families to visit the desert. You can see the snow-covered mountains in Wrightwood and learn about winter sports. If you visit in the right time, you will see the San Bernardino County Fair. It is a fun event. The Victor Valley Museum shows us the history of our town and the desert.

My neighborhood is different from most. I do not live in a house with a family. I live in a school. The school is like a neighborhood with many people. It has buildings, people, stores, and a park.

Let's talk about the buildings first. There are three kinds of buildings in my school. There are apartments, houses, and dormitories. Apartments have 2-4 people in each room. There are 4-6 rooms on each floor. One building usually has 2 floors and about 20 people live there. Some houses have 2-4 bedrooms and are rented by school alumni. There are not many of these houses. Most people live in dormitories. A dormitory is a building with many rooms. Two people share a room, but sometimes there are only one person in a room.

The people in my school come from many different cultures and ages. The school staff lives in houses, new students live in dormitories, and older students live in apartments. Let's talk about the stores now. My school has many stores. You can find food, clothes, and other things you need. The park is a nice place for everyone to play. It is clean and safe because everyone takes care of it.

My school is its own neighborhood. You can get everything you need inside the school boundaries. This is a special place.

I have lived in this neighborhood for about 10 years. When I first came, I was sad. I missed my old home in Riverdale. But my parents wanted a better life for me and my sister. We moved to a new house in a good area with a good school.

Over time, I got to know some new friends and some people I did not like. My neighbors were kind to me, especially Mr. Glen and his family. We had fun together, like when we went to his wedding. I caught a special strap Ms. Veda wore on her leg, but I missed catching the flowers! We danced and had a good time.

The neighborhood is like a big maze. Now I have a GPS, so I can explore it. I like to play video games with my friends Kason and Curtis. We also play games outside, like in the park. The park is nice and calm. It makes me feel peaceful.

I like to bring sticks from the store and practice my balance. I also like to bring my wooden sword and have fun. There is a basketball and tennis court, but I do not play as much as I used to. My dad taught me tennis when I was younger. I had fun playing with him.

I have many good memories in this neighborhood. I hope I will have more in the future.

I live near the college I attend. I like this place. Many apartment buildings are here, some restaurants and bars too. The bars are not very expensive. One bar is new, but it is not very good. Many people are friendly. They are college students or work in lower income jobs. The housing is not very expensive. There is a school near my apartment. Many children live here. I do not know my neighbors. They smoke a lot of marijuana. My building managers put a freshener near their door. It is funny. 

The buildings near me are old but maybe nice inside. A little further down the street are new apartments. I do not like them. They are not well built but cost a lot. The restaurant near me is cheap. They serve food on paper plates and heat it in a microwave. Across from the restaurant is a gas station. It is not a good place to work. But the city fixed the road near my apartment. Now it is nicer. My apartment building has many trees. The city cut some down, but I like the trees. Behind my building are more trees and another apartment complex. The street behind my building is not very nice. The sidewalks are bad and the buildings look old. Many trees hide the buildings' bad looks. There is crime on this street. One apartment complex has a lot of problems. But I like where I live. It is close to the university and I can walk there. There are bus stops nearby too.

My neighborhood is made up of two-house houses on a closed street. The houses are placed far apart and look like separate houses. They are all painted yellow with white porches and green roofs. Most people like each other, but not everyone. We stand at the end of a street some evenings and talk while the small children play outside. It is a nice change from our busy world. It is like going back in time. We are near fields and trees with blue skies and white clouds. 

There is one problem. This season, we have had tornado warnings. One night we heard the warning sirens, and we went to a safe place. My little dog and I went into the bathtub, and my big dog stayed in the living room. The storm was loud, and we could hear big hail hitting the ground. After the storm, the street was hot from the change in temperature. The hail melted when it hit the hot pavement. The sky started to clear, and the sun came out. I saw a beautiful rainbow. I took pictures to share with my friends on Facebook. They were happy, like I was. The people in the neighborhood were quiet for a while after the storm. Then they went back to their normal activities, like cooking dinner. I like this neighborhood because it is friendly. I moved here from New Hampshire to North Carolina. I like the way people talk in the South. I have a two-bedroom apartment like most people. But the apartments are different inside. Some are small. I like to walk in the big field behind my house and visit the small pond. I see deer and hear a big frog singing in the morning. This is a great place to live, just 40 minutes from Charlotte. I like hearing the roosters crowing in the morning. It is like living in a small village. We even have a donkey that brays in the evening. I am lucky to live here.

I moved to this neighborhood when I was about to start eighth grade. It was hard to make friends at first. I made friends with two people who lived near me. They no longer live here, but I still think about them. The people who lived here when I first moved here are still living here. My neighborhood is normal. It has many two-story houses. You can hear kids playing outside on weekends. The neighborhood is quiet most days. I have never had problems with my neighbors. I feel safe here. They leave me alone unless I need help. I ordered packages online and they were always safe. I trust my neighbors.

There is a park near my house. I have many happy memories there. I played basketball, football, and baseball with my friends. I also got hurt playing football, but the good memories are more important. Now, I go to the park with my cousin's kids. They like playing on swings and slides. The park makes me happy. The neighborhood is different from others. You can find many kinds of food here. There are Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian restaurants near here. But many people now use apps to get food delivered. There is a grocery store, Walgreens, CVS, and dry cleaners near here. There is also an Indian store where you can buy Indian food. I like my neighborhood. I see bad things on social media and news about some people's neighbors. I am happy with mine.

My neighborhood is a small town. It is in South Carolina. Johnston is a special place. It is called the Peach Capital of the World. This is what the town says on its welcome sign. Most of Johnston is farmland with peach trees or cattle. Some houses are far apart from the main part of town. They are usually two stories high with metal or gray roofs to keep cool. Most houses are not near the road. They are behind the houses, used for animals and crops.

In the main part of town, there is a stop light at a four-way intersection. This is where you can find the town's stores. There are three places to get fast food. One is a small Chinese restaurant called Hong Kong. Another is a Mexican restaurant called Fiesta. The third is a small burger place called Gary's. There used to be a pizza place, but it closed.

There is a small family-owned pharmacy called Maxwell and Halford Drug. They are famous for selling Cherry Coca-Cola. The only grocery store in town is called IGA. People usually don't buy much here. They like to go to a big store in a nearby town called Walmart. The most popular store in Johnston is Dollar General. They sell many common things and it is always busy.

There is a small furniture store called Possibilities Furniture & More. It has been in Johnston for a long time. The owner is a kind woman. She also employs people to help move furniture. Next to the furniture store is a pet grooming shop called Clark's Cuts. They take care of pets, including feeding, boarding, and grooming.

The doctor's office and the veterinarian are not in the main part of town. They are small, but they can help the people of Johnston. There is one elementary school called Johnston Elementary. When students finish fifth grade, they go to school in the next town. Johnston is small. There are no parks, but they are building a new place for families to play.

There is not much to do in Johnston. There are no movie theaters, bowling alleys, or places for people to hang out. But it is a nice town. You can easily miss it if you blink.

I first heard about my neighborhood on a podcast about people who disappeared. This was surprising to me. Almost every apartment in the area costs more than one thousand dollars a month. I had never heard this story before and neither had my friends. Maybe it's because we are struggling. I know some of my friends cry at night because things are expensive. We have learned to be careful with money. We like used things. We like the smell of old toys and clothes that are not used. As people get older, we smell less. We might start to smoke or be used to how things are. But the flea market always reminds us of this. The smell of old magazines on a piano is strong. It stays in the leather even after we wash it. There are three used stores near my home. One is on the far side and has two stores that help charity, a library, a store with old books, and a store with strange things. The streets are very crowded in the city center. Cars and people are everywhere in the morning. But we can't hear the noise in the used stores. Many people and cars go by, but the stores are quiet. It's a nice place to spend an afternoon. More and more people come here every year. The city is growing. It's a big city with one of the biggest internet companies. It's still not perfect. It reminds me of New York. People are focused on their goals and don't ask many questions. We can be alone if we want and people will leave us alone. It's different from the South, where people ask if you care. We can keep to ourselves here and the city will move around us like the ocean waves. This is a lively place to live. There is music near my home. A person plays the piano next door and two people sing upstairs. We come together for important things, like birthdays and help each other when we can. I'm lucky to live here. I like most of my neighbors and they are kind to me. We help each other and leave food for each other. We take care of each other's mail. It's nice to see them and I think they like me too. I live in a big, modern city, but my neighbors make me feel like I'm not alone.

I live in a common type of neighborhood. Many people in my area have well-maintained homes. The homes are all very similar. They have green grass, small stones, and short driveways. Some have small trees. Every house has two cars. The streets are in good condition. There are no holes in the road. Most homes are one story, but some are two stories.

There are shared mailboxes at the end of the street. Everyone uses a key to get their mail. There are also two big boxes for packages. The neighborhood is near the edge of the city, so it feels like the country and the suburbs. We have a lot of space. There are swimming pools that everyone can use. They are safe and well-maintained. We also have paths where people can walk their dogs or go for a walk.

Most people living here are older. It is a safe place. People look out for each other. We also have some middle-aged and young people. The city is big, but it feels small. We have many things that people need. We have a small mall with many stores. It takes me 15 minutes to drive to the mall. There are many stores with different kinds of food and other things. We have places to buy expensive food and cheap food. My neighborhood is safe, clean, and good. We have nice things like pools and paths. It is easy to get to other places by car.

I live in a small town in the Midwest. It is near a big city. My neighborhood is on the east side of town. It is an area with lower incomes. People who own homes in this area mostly rent or buy them. The houses are not expensive. However, the neighborhood is not unattractive. People are friendly. They say hello when I walk by. There is a little more crime here than in other areas of town. There have been a few bad incidents near my home. My next-door neighbors lost their son in a shooting last year. However, my family has not been hurt by crime. Sometimes we lose small things from our porch if we forget to bring them inside. Our town is affected by a big problem called the opioid epidemic. Many people have died from overdoses. There are many places to help people who are struggling with addiction. The town has good schools. My son's school is excellent. The staff is kind and helpful. My son has a special need, but he is not bullied. The school has a good atmosphere. The teachers and staff do their best to help all students. The school provides food for all students so they do not go hungry. No family is treated unfairly because they cannot pay. The town government has made some changes to improve our town. They have fixed roads, planted trees, and improved the parks. Unfortunately, most of these changes happened in the center of town and on the west side. I like living in this town. People are friendly, the schools are great, and there are many stores to buy things we need. Our home is not worth much, but it is comfortable. We have lived here for over 16 years. We do not want to live anywhere else.

My neighborhood is very interesting. It's on a hill and has many old buildings. I live in a big apartment building. It's across from a old theater and near a park. People like to go to a cool bar in the park area at night. The park is big for our area. It has a wall with stairs. During the cold months, homeless people set up their tents in rows on the sidewalk and stairs. They do this to stay warm. The rain in our area is heavier than the snow, so it's hard to stay warm. They stay together for warmth and can easily walk to a place where they can wash themselves.

I like my neighborhood. It's not just the old buildings and hills that I like. I like the people. Our neighborhood used to be very bad. There was a lot of violence. The government and police had to come in to clean it up. The people remember this. They still tell stories about it. They work hard to keep their neighborhood clean. They care about what happens in their neighborhood. Some people say white people should not walk around at night. I think this is because of the past. I am not white, but I can pass for white. I think the people in my neighborhood see me as one of them. They are kind to me. They are not mean. People in my neighborhood help each other. A store owner stayed open late so I could charge my phone. Someone gave me money and told me I'm beautiful.

I live in a small town in Michigan. It is a quiet place. I like it because it is close to water. I live near two big lakes, Lake Michigan and Lake Charlevoix. You can swim in these lakes.

My town is not a big city. I do not see big stores like Walmart or Target. We have to drive to get to any store. My neighborhood is special. Houses are not the same. They are old and new, some have been updated. There are many colors of houses. Most houses have yards with trampolines and playsets for kids. Some people have gardens and fences for their animals.

Hardworking people live here. They work to make a living and raise families. You can see kids playing outside and people walking dogs or riding bikes. Neighbors know each other and say hello. The lawns are kept clean. The grass is mowed and looks nice.

It is a safe place to live. The county sheriff's office and jail are near my house. We have a recycling center where people bring their trash. There are baseball fields where you can hear the announcers calling the game. Small planes fly overhead. I can walk to the ice cream shop and to the park. My kids can ride their bikes to the park, which is just a few blocks away. It is a great place to live.
